## Priority Matrix

### P0 — Immediate (this week)

| Action | Effort | Impact |
|--------|--------|--------|
| Sticky header: phone tap-to-call + primary CTA | 2h | Conversion lift |
| WebP conversion + hero preload | 4h | LCP 30-50% improvement |
| FAQ page с schema markup | Low | SEO + trust |

### P1 — This month

| Action | Effort | Impact |
|--------|--------|--------|
| Portfolio как story-driven project pages | 1-2 days | Trust + engagement |
| Materials page с swatch grid | 1 day | Lead gen |
| Before/after sliders | 2h | Visual proof |
| 2 blog posts/month (ET, material guides) | Medium | Organic traffic |
| Structured data (LocalBusiness + Product) | 4h | Rich results 2-4 weeks |

### P2 — This quarter

| Action | Effort | Impact |
|--------|--------|--------|
| Instagram: carousel-first + Reels | Low | Engagement |
| Pinterest boards + n8n auto-pin | Medium | Long-term traffic |
| Email nurture sequence (6 emails) | Medium | Lead conversion |
| Security headers | 2h | Baseline hardening |
| NextGEN pagination + pre-generated thumbs | 4h | Gallery page load |

### P3 — When free

| Action | Effort | Impact |
|--------|--------|--------|
| Monthly newsletter | Low | Retention |
| FI localization key pages | Low | Niche high-value leads |
| 360 showroom tour (Matterport) | $300 | Nice-to-have |
| Moodboard/favorites feature | 1-2 days | Engagement |

---

*Compiled: 2026-04-11. Sources: Poggenpohl, SieMatic, Bulthaup, Nolte, Haecker analysis + industry research (MarketKeep, BrightLocal, Schema.org, Semrush, Crazy Egg, Request Metrics).*
